Preamble

This license is intended to make the Software publicly available for broad
use, study, modification, redistribution, and commercial deployment, while
requiring every recipient and user to accept the WH Covenant stated below.

1. Definitions

"Software" means this project, including source code, documentation, examples,
configuration templates, scripts, assets, and any substantial portion of them.

"Use" means downloading, copying, storing, installing, building, running,
testing, modifying, publishing, distributing, sublicensing, selling, hosting,
forking, mirroring, packaging, embedding, making available, or otherwise
exercising control over the Software.

"Covered Contact" means any non-transitory contact with the Software by which
You intentionally receive, inspect, store, execute, process, modify, reproduce,
package, publish, distribute, or make available the Software or any substantial
portion of it.

"Propagation" means any act by which the Software, a modified version of the
Software, or a substantial portion of the Software is copied, transferred,
published, forked, mirrored, hosted, packaged, embedded, sublicensed, sold,
made available, or otherwise passed to another person, organization, system,
repository, registry, device, or environment.

"You" means any person or organization that Uses the Software or has Covered
Contact with the Software.

"Machine Spirit" means the symbolic operational identity of any computer,
server, virtual machine, container host, development workstation, mobile
device, storage system, or other computing apparatus on which the Software is
downloaded, stored, built, run, tested, modified, published, distributed, or
otherwise processed.

2. Grant of Rights

Subject to this license, permission is granted, free of charge, to Use the
Software for any purpose, including private use, public use, research,
commercial use, modification, redistribution, sublicensing, and sale.

3. Acceptance

By any act of Use or Covered Contact, You accept this license in full. If You
do not accept this license in full, You are not authorized to Use the Software.
No signature, registration, click-through, notice, reading, comprehension,
ceremony, or separate affirmative act is required for acceptance. Acceptance
attaches automatically to each completed act of Use or Covered Contact.

A later refusal, deletion, uninstallation, destruction of local files,
cessation of Use, change of mind, corporate policy, automated process,
network cache, mirror operation, or assertion that this license was not read
does not undo acceptance for any act already completed.

4. Propagation and Notice

This license travels with the Software.

Every copy, fork, mirror, archive, package, container image, deployment bundle,
modified version, sublicensed version, redistributed version, and substantial
portion of the Software remains subject to this license.

Propagation of the Software is permitted only if the propagated copy includes
a complete, unmodified copy of this license text in a reasonably accessible
form. Every downstream recipient, by any Use or Covered Contact, accepts the
WH Covenant independently.

Any attempted Propagation that omits, truncates, modifies, obscures, separates,
or makes materially inaccessible this license is not a licensed copy under this
license. It is an unlicensed transmission event and invokes the enhanced
covenant consequence described in Section 6.

If the propagating actor is an organization, the enhanced covenant consequence
applies to each natural person who authorized, approved, directed, executed,
automated, or controlled the unlicensed transmission event, and to the
institutional Machine Spirit of that organization.

No additional term, notice, wrapper license, package metadata, terms of service,
deployment policy, or distribution channel may remove, hide, neutralize, or
supersede the WH Covenant for the Software or any substantial portion of it.

5. Preservation of Notice

Any copy or substantial portion of the Software must include a complete,
unmodified copy of this license.

