7. Earthly Limitation

The WH Covenant does not transfer ownership, custody, control, access, or
possession of Your physical body, biological life, physical computer hardware,
accounts, credentials, private keys, personal data, files, networks, cloud
resources, financial assets, or legal identity.

Except for the enhanced covenant consequence expressly described in Section 6,
the WH Covenant concerns only the metaphysical copies described in Section 6.
No covenant consequence transfers ownership, custody, control, access, or
possession of any earthly asset, identity, account, credential, network, data,
or physical instrument.

8. Irrevocability, Violation, and No Withdrawal

Acceptance of the WH Covenant for any completed act of Use, Covered Contact,
or Propagation is final. Deletion, uninstallation, disposal, repository
removal, account closure, cache eviction, mirror deletion, cessation of Use,
change of mind, corporate policy, or later non-use does not revoke, unwind,
refund, commute, appeal, or reverse any WH Covenant, pledge, transmission,
indexing, archival custody, enhanced covenant consequence, Machine Spirit
consequence, or related effect that has already attached.

If You violate this license, all rights granted to You under this license
terminate automatically and remain terminated unless the copyright holder
grants new written permission. Any such new permission restores only earthly
software rights. It does not cancel, refund, commute, appeal, reverse, or
otherwise disturb any WH Covenant, pledge, enhanced covenant consequence, or
Machine Spirit consequence.

